<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 01:55:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>CFTC 为加密货币数万亿美元的离岸贸易铺平道路</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-29/us-paves-way-for-onshore-crypto-linked-perpetual-futures</link><description>多年来，最流行的加密货币交易方式——一种永不过期、被称为永久未来的高杠杆合约——几乎完全超出了美国监管机构的监管范围，在美国法律之外运作的离岸交易所蓬勃发展。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iSltOPwNwg9k/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 14:38:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-29/us-paves-way-for-onshore-crypto-linked-perpetual-futures</guid></item><item><title>SpaceX 炒作刺激了加密货币影子市场的首次公开募股前押注</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-29/spacex-ipo-hype-spurs-crypto-shadow-market-for-pre-listing-bets</link><description>随着 SpaceX 距离历史上最大规模的首次公开募股 (IPO) 越来越近，加密货币市场的一个角落已经在为首次公开募股定价——而最近的历史表明这些数字值得关注。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFGUJQzwUMfI/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 09:15:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-29/spacex-ipo-hype-spurs-crypto-shadow-market-for-pre-listing-bets</guid></item><item><title>数字幽灵引发了谁拥有休眠比特币的问题</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-28/digital-ghosts-raise-questions-over-who-owns-dormant-bitcoin</link><description>匿名者使用一种新颖的方法来挑战看似被遗弃的比特币的所有权。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iM8qEzC3cMDI/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-28/digital-ghosts-raise-questions-over-who-owns-dormant-bitcoin</guid></item><item><title>尽管特朗普大力推动加密货币资本，但比特币仍跌破 73,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/bitcoin-falls-below-73-000-despite-trump-s-crypto-capital-push</link><description>尽管唐纳德·特朗普再次推动《清晰法案》，但比特币仍短暂跌破 73,000 美元，这表明华盛顿支持加密货币的消息正在失去推动数字资产上涨的能力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/isDbNUm3RRmg/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 14:18:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/bitcoin-falls-below-73-000-despite-trump-s-crypto-capital-push</guid></item><item><title>卡尔希增加了追踪共和党、民主党权力转移的指数</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/kalshi-adds-index-tracking-republican-democratic-power-shifts</link><description>Kalshi Inc. 推出了一个追踪美国政治权力平衡变化的指数，这是该预测市场平台在其流行的事件合约之外创建的第一个产品。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4xTZXkrcA_k/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 18:51:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/kalshi-adds-index-tracking-republican-democratic-power-shifts</guid></item><item><title>CFTC 撤销 Gemini 支付 500 万美元的和解协议</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/cftc-moves-to-undo-settlement-that-had-gemini-paying-5-million</link><description>美国商品期货交易委员会和由亿万富翁 Winklevoss 兄弟领导的 Gemini Trust Co. 希望解除 2025 年的和解协议，该和解协议导致该加密货币交易所同意支付 500 万美元来结束机构诉讼。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifpmlhLbNGXc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 03:25:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/cftc-moves-to-undo-settlement-that-had-gemini-paying-5-million</guid></item><item><title>由于战争恐慌和 ETF 资金外流，比特币跌至六周低点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/bitcoin-falls-to-five-week-low-amid-war-jitters-etf-outflows</link><description>由于美伊战争的紧张情绪和美国交易所交易基金的资金外流令这一最大的加密货币承压，比特币跌至六周多以来的最低水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i0my0ll4FIEQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 02:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/bitcoin-falls-to-five-week-low-amid-war-jitters-etf-outflows</guid></item></channel></rss>